<h2>Homebrew (macOS / Linux)</h2>

<p>The fastest way to install and keep PgDesigner up to date:</p>

<pre><code>brew tap vmkteam/tap
brew install pgdesigner</code></pre>

<p>Update to the latest version:</p>

<pre><code>brew upgrade pgdesigner</code></pre>

